data.text:
THE CLAUDIA DEAN DIFFERENCE

At Claudia Dean World our mission is simple, to welcome all dancers into our positive and uplifting community, and support them wherever they are in their ballet journey with nurturing ballet coaching, exclusive ballet courses, dancewear, activewear, accessories and so much more!

ABOUT CLAUDIA DEAN

Claudia Dean is an Australian Dancer and the Founder and Director of Claudia Dean World. After joining the Royal Ballet School in London in 2009, Claudia was one of 6 Australian Dancers who graduated with this prestigious honour and was accepted into The Royal Ballet Company. Claudia retired in 2014 and moved back to Australia to pursue her passion of coaching the next generation of dancers and in 2015 Claudia Dean World was officially born. Since 2015, Claudia has expanded the business from private one-on-one private ballet coaching into a global brand that inspires and empowers dancers with ballet coaching, online ballet coaching, dancewear for kids and adults, activewear for kids and adults, online ballet courses, ballet technique tips, a ballet focused podcast and a ballet technique app.

ABOUT CLAUDIA DEAN COACHING

Claudia Dean is renowned for her private ballet coaching, which she started in 2015. What started as single one-on-one ballet coaching in a small studio space in Brisbane, Australia has since grown into a global community of like-minded-dancers, who can’t get enough of Claudia’s holistic, nurturing and engaging approach to technical skill development. Claudia Dean Coaching is designed to make all dancers feel like they’re part of a safe, positive and supportive community and is accessible to dancers all over the world through private ballet coaching, Claudia Dean Ballet Technique Tours, The Claudia Dean Ballet App, Claudia Dean Online Ballet Courses and so much more.

ABOUT Claudia Dean Collections

Claudia Dean Collections was founded in 2017 and started as a bespoke collection of comfortable and fashionable leotards and ballet dancewear. After developing a loyal following of dancers who couldn’t get enough of the bright colours and comfortable designs, Claudia Dean Collections has expanded to now include activewear, dance accessories, shoes, bags and so much more. Claudia Dean Collections are stocked in over 80 locations across Australia, New Zealand, China, The US, Canada and Europe and releases 12 collections every single year, becoming thousands of dancers go-to dance wear brand right around the world.
